s'', offer: ''increase sales by 20%'', CTA: ''15-minute chat next week''). Decided to craft a personalized email addressing their specific pain point and proposing the CTA.\\n2. **Act:** Delegated the email drafting task to the Email Copywriter with all necessary context, including the lead''s details and the desired outcome.\\n3. **Finalize:** Received and reviewed the drafted email from the Email Copywriter, ensuring it met the criteria of being personalized, concise, and action-oriented."}', null), ('5', '2025-07-22 15:56:23.561847+00', 'f7ee9f97-dead-4f92-99de-23cd707e3f0c', 'b4e85802-1d5c-49b8-9b64-be68a40272c7', null, null, null, null, null, '1', '19832d728680c6cd', '{"lead_id":1,"drafted_reply":"**Subject:** Quick question—could we help you generate 20% more leads?\\n\\nHi Chris,\\n\\nI noticed Summit Lead Generation Ltd is doing great work in the lead gen space—impressive stuff! But I also know how tough it can be when the pipeline isn’t as full as you’d like.\\n\\nWhat if we could help you increase sales by 20%? We’ve worked with companies like yours to refine their outreach and fill their funnel with high-quality leads—without the usual headaches.\\n\\nI’d love to hop on a quick 15-minute call next week to explore how we might be able to help. No pressure, just a chat to see if there’s a fit.\\n\\nDoes Tuesday at 2 PM work for you? If not, let me know a time that does—I’ll make it easy.\\n\\nLooking forward to your thoughts,\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Position]\\n[Your Company]\\n[Your Email]\\n[Your Phone Number]\\n\\nP.S. If now’s not the right time, no worries—just say the word, and I’ll circle back in a few months.","agent_reasoning":"1. **Plan:** The lead, Chris Hall, is the director at Summit Lead Generation Ltd with a pain point of ''not enough leads''. Our offer is to ''increase sales by 20%'' with a CTA to schedule a 15-minute chat. The email needed to be personalized, address the pain point, and propose a clear next step.\\n2. **Act:** Attempted to enrich company data using the Company Profile Enrichment Tool, but no data was returned. Delegated the email drafting task to the Email Copywriter with all available context.\\n3. **Finalize:** The Email Copywriter provided a concise, friendly, and personalized email draft that directly addresses the lead''s pain point and includes a clear CTA for a 15-minute chat."}', null), ('6', '2025-07-23 13:29:45.222986+00', 'f7ee9f97-dead-4f92-99de-23cd707e3f0c', 'b4e85802-1d5c-49b8-9b64-be68a40272c7', null, null, null, null, null, '1', '1983778846159077', '{"lead_id":1,"drafted_reply":"**Subject:** Quick Chat to Boost Your Lead Pipeline?\\n\\nHi Chris,\\n\\nI noticed Summit Lead Generation Ltd is facing a common challenge—not enough leads to hit your growth targets. That’s frustrating, especially when you know the demand is out there but just out of reach.\\n\\nHere’s the good news: we’ve helped companies like yours increase sales by 20% by optimizing their lead generation strategies. It’s not magic—just a few proven tweaks to attract and convert more high-quality prospects.\\n\\nWould you be open to a quick 15-minute chat next week? I’d love to explore how we could help you fill your pipeline with the right leads. Let me know a time that works for you—I’ll adapt to your schedule.\\n\\nLooking forward to your thoughts,\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Position]\\n[Your Company]\\n[Your Contact Information]\\n\\nP.S. If now’s not the right time, no worries—just say the word, and I’ll circle back later.","agent_reasoning":"1. **Plan:** The lead, Chris Hall, is the director at Summit Lead Generation Ltd with a pain point of ''not enough leads''. Our offer is to ''increase sales by 20%'' with a CTA to schedule a 15-minute chat next week. The plan was to draft a personalized email addressing these points.\\n2. **Act:** Attempted to enrich company data using the Company Profile Enrichment Tool, but no data was returned. Delegated the email drafting task to the Email Copywriter with all available context.\\n3. **Finalize:** Received a concise, personalized email draft from the Email Copywriter that directly addresses the lead''s pain point, offers a solution, and includes a clear CTA with a professional yet approachable tone."}', null), ('7', '2025-07-23 13:31:09.960986+00', 'f7ee9f97-dead-4f92-99de-23cd707e3f0c', 'b4e85802-1d5c-49b8-9b64-be68a40272c7', null, null, null, null, null, '1', '1983778846159077', '{"lead_id":1,"drafted_reply":"**Subject:** Quick Chat to Boost Your Lead Pipeline?\\n\\nHi Chris,\\n\\nI noticed Summit Lead Generation Ltd is in the business of driving high-quality leads—yet, like many in the industry, you might be hitting a wall with \\"not enough leads\\" to hit your growth targets.\\n\\nWhat if we could help you turn that around and increase sales by 20%?\\n\\nI’d love to hop on a quick 15-minute call next week to explore how we’ve helped similar companies unlock consistent lead flow and scale their revenue. Would Tuesday at 2 PM or Thursday at 11 AM work for you?\\n\\nLooking forward to your thoughts!\\n\\nBest,\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Position]\\n[Your Company]\\n[Your Contact Information]\\n\\nP.S. If timing’s tight, just reply with a better slot—I’ll make it work.","agent_reasoning":"1. **Plan:** The lead, Chris Hall, is the director at Summit Lead Generation Ltd with a pain point of ''not enough leads''. Our offer is to ''increase sales by 20%'' with a CTA to schedule a ''15-minute chat next week''. Since the Company Profile Enrichment Tool didn''t return additional data, I proceeded with the available information.\\n2. **Act:** Delegated the task of drafting a personalized email to the Email Copywriter, providing all necessary context about the lead and the desired outcome.\\n3. **Finalize:** The Email Copywriter crafted a concise, personalized email addressing the lead''s pain point, offering a solution, and proposing specific times for a follow-up call. The email includes a PS for flexibility to increase response likelihood."}', null), ('8', '2025-07-23 13:45:09.300796+00', 'f7ee9f97-dead-4f92-99de-23cd707e3f0c', 'b4e85802-1d5c-49b8-9b64-be68a40272c7', 'neutral', 'follow_up', 'The lead did not reply to the email, indicating no clear interest or disinterest. A follow-up is needed to re-engage.', null, 'Hi Chris, I noticed you didn’t respond to my last email. I’d love to hear your thoughts on how we can help you increase sales by 20%. Are you free for a quick 15-minute chat next week?', '1', '19837879c2d12df3', '{"action":"follow_up","lead_id":1,"summary":"The lead did not reply to the email, indicating no clear interest or disinterest. A follow-up is needed to re-engage.","sentiment":"neutral","nextStepPrompt":"Hi Chris, I noticed you didn’t respond to my last email. I’d love to hear your thoughts on how we can help you increase sales by 20%. Are you free for a quick 15-minute chat next week?"}', null), ('9', '2025-07-23 13:45:24.136298+00', 'f7ee9f97-dead-4f92-99de-23cd707e3f0c', 'b4e85802-1d5c-49b8-9b64-be68a40272c7', 'neutral', 'follow_up', 'The lead did not reply to the email, indicating no clear interest or disinterest. A follow-up is needed to re-engage.', null, 'Hi Chris, I noticed you haven’t responded to my previous email about increasing your sales by 20%. Are you still interested in exploring how we can help you generate more leads? Let me know if you’d like to schedule a quick 15-minute chat next week.', '1', '198378656970b458', '{"action":"follow_up","lead_id":1,"summary":"The lead did not reply to the email, indicating no clear interest or disinterest. A follow-up is needed to re-engage.","sentiment":"neutral","nextStepPrompt":"Hi Chris, I noticed you haven’t responded to my previous email about increasing your sales by 20%. Are you still interested in exploring how we can help you generate more leads? Let me know if you’d like to schedule a quick 15-minute chat next week."}', null), ('10', '2025-07-23 13:47:25.105615+00', 'f7ee9f97-dead-4f92-99de-23cd707e3f0c', 'b4e85802